
About
=====

This is the patch for allowing the acAclPolicy rule access to the username variable.

Note: only works for irods login (ie not for GSI, Kerberos.)

Applying
========

Copy the .patch file into the root iRODS/ source directory, and in that directory run:

patch -p0 -i aclpolicy_username.patch

Then recompile/install the server.
